'''The Shelter''' was home to the 25 descendants of a survey team to [[Dagobah/Legends|Dagobah]]. A small island of dry ground, it held between 20 and 30 huts. The huts were made of dried mud, with roofs formed from [[Gnarltree/Legends|gnarlwood]] branches coated with slime.

In the center of the village was an open shelter without any walls. Inside it, the Children kept the broken log of the original survey team.

